article_title: Here are the results – The Denver Post
article_text:
Do plants have feelings? Does Denver’s corpse flower know how special it is? Can anyone place the Denver Botanic Gardens on a map? The first two questions we can guess at, but the third, we know. More than 400 people attempted to place Denver Botanic Gardens on a map this week, and more than 100 (28.2%) got it right.
